Usage: bindKey [-help] [<key>] [<cmd>] [<isPublic>]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<key>                     # Specifies the key to use as the shortcut.
                          # (string, optional)
<cmd>                     # Specifies the command to be executed when key is
                          # pressed. (string, optional)
<isPublic>                # Specifies the bindkey as user defined
                          # (string, optional)